Author: anonymousthrowawayed
Text: I felt really weird tbh like too full then super sluggish then really wired. All I want to do atm is just not eat anything so I’m hoping maybe that’ll hold up. I’ll try remember all that if I get the urge to binge

Text: How did you feel physically after eating that whole pizza? I'd try to remember that too-full feeling when the impulse is strong.
